        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "7e51",
          "text": "On September 17th, 2011 (more than six years ago), Occupy Wall Street spread like a media virus around the world. Many thought it would harken the transition to global democracy. There was an Arab Spring, an African Awakening, and the feeling of inevitability continued to grow.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
