              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 203,
              "href": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arab_Spring",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 192,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 225,
              "href": "https://www.amazon.com/African-Awakening-Revolutions-Sokari-Ekine/dp/0857490214",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 208,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a566",
          "text": "Fast forward to today, December 2nd, 2017, when the slogan “We are the 99%” rings hollow as the plutocrats representing the top 0.1% pass legislation in the United States to revoke the estate tax (so all of that hoarded wealth remains in their private coffers through future generations); shift tax burdens onto graduate students (to expand the debt labor pool longer in time for the working classes); and add another huge load to the national debt (which represents a tax on future generations).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "52bc",
          "text": "Note how this was done through orchestrated “institution building” that spans many decades. On August 23, 1971 the famous Powell Memo was drafted to outline the plan for the billionaire class to build a network of think tanks, infiltrate universities with endowed faculty positions, buy up and consolidate media, create organizations like ALEC that produce template legislation that can be replicated from state to state across the country, and so on.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 133,
              "href": "http://reclaimdemocracy.org/powell_memo_lewis/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 122,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a133",
          "text": "Contrast this with the fervor of unleashed moral indignation by those using social media to attack anyone they see as “the enemy” — a frame that replaces itself with such dizzying speed that literally every week for the last three years we have had a new threat to reckon with. This meshwork of activities has polarized and divided us, having been orchestrated by what is called psychographic marketing (or targeted ads based on psychological profiles as a way to segment audiences).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8042",
          "text": "One change strategy involved the coordination of action around the accumulation of institutional power. The other change strategy involved dividing people into memetic tribes and fighting with each other.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0d3d",
          "text": "Today we see which one was successful. Let this sink in.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "3b8175ce38dd_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c775",
          "text": "Onward, fellow humans.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
